      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0350P0-04297'>
        <a name='S6CV0350P0_20000523_WH_23'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tony-worthington' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0350P0_20000523_WH_23' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tony Worthington' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
